				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Jaheira's eldest is giving the youngest son some encouragement and trying to get him to be at ease. He's not biologically related to Jaheira's family, but has been taken in after an unknown traumatic incident with his family.\r\nRion's approach is not to soften her tone too much or soothe him - just to treat him like everything he's doing and feeling is normal."
				}
